00:17:30,500 --> 00:17:31,740
Adakah kamu cukup berkuasa?

267
00:17:32,340 --> 00:17:33,500
Kelakar.

268
00:17:34,220 --> 00:17:36,180
Di Kota Raya, siapa berani halang saya?

