00:18:32,020 --> 00:18:32,860
Baiklah.

294
00:18:33,020 --> 00:18:33,860
Mari kita pergi.

295
00:18:34,500 --> 00:18:35,340
- Yueling.
- Yang Mulia.

296
00:18:40,500 --> 00:18:41,340
Tuanku,

297
00:18:41,420 --> 00:18:44,180
Puteri Ashina Zhu ada di sini untuk bertemu dengan tuanku.

298
00:18:46,980 --> 00:18:48,740
Bukankah dia dikurung di rumah agam Shiyu?

299
00:18:49,700 --> 00:18:51,740
Putera Selatan membawanya ke sini.

