334
00:20:22,900 --> 00:20:23,820
Apa maksud kamu?

335
00:20:24,540 --> 00:20:27,740
Tuanku, tolong izinkan saya
pergi ke Liuzhou untuk Putera Utara.

336
00:20:31,300 --> 00:20:33,060
Kamu bangun dulu.

337
00:20:33,540 --> 00:20:35,060
Tolong luluskan, Tuanku.

